  <h3>‚úî Do‚Äôs</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Practice rainwater harvesting.</li>
    <li>Turn off taps tightly after every use.</li>
    <li>Store water safely to avoid contamination.</li>
    <li>Share water with animals and plants.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>‚ùå Don‚Äôts</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Do NOT waste water while washing vehicles.</li>
    <li>Do NOT leave taps running.</li>
    <li>Do NOT grow water-hungry crops during drought periods.</li>
    <li>Do NOT use borewells excessively.</li>
  </ul>
</article>

